headline: Agilent Presents Solutions Innovation Research Awards to Institut National de la Recherche Scientifique and University of Southern California Scientists
summary: SANTA CLARA, Calif., November 06, 2024--Agilent Technologies Inc. (NYSE: A) today announced that Professor Isabelle Plante at Institut National de la Recherche Scientifique (INRS), and Professor Bangyan Stiles at the University of Southern California (USC) are recipients of an Agilent Solutions Innovation Research Award (SIRA). The honorees will receive separate awards on behalf of their institutions in recognition of their research in cell and gene therapy.
